      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAV REIKO (2) produced a moderate performance last time when fifth at this track over 515m behind Sparring (30.03) in a Mix 3/4. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and two minor placings from six starts. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. EXTREME GRUNT (6) finished in the minors last time but only a few starts back broke the clock when winning over 515m at this track, taking a Grade 5 in an outstanding 29.34. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. ASTON BUGSY (7) placed in a Free For All last time, colliding in the run and finishing a 6 length third over 520m at Cannington. Has two wins from Box 7. Worth following up. UNWORLDLY (8) has been going along well and was strongly fancied last time but could only manage second (29.49) at Mt Gambier. Won at his only start from this box.",
